    "body": "> No support for string in the array of indices?\n\nYou mean only specifying the index names like: `index, index_priceASC, ..`?\n\nI don't see it as an easier way or sugar. When would you not want a label that is different from the index name? Using the algolia index name as a direct displaying string is a bit weird, did you see any implementation doing it?\n",
