  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think we can let the user define its own custom `template` for this widget (and the searchBox) so they can add whatever classes or attributes they want, but we need to check that they are resp. `<select>` and `<input type=\"text\">` elements.\n\nThis way, we can still correctly bind our click event to the correct dom element, while letting the user customize it.\n",
